[[Translation:Main/en/Wagon speed limits]]
{{en/-}}
Sets whether speed limits should apply for wagons that set them. The default wagons in the game do not specify a maximum speed, so this feature only affects wagons from [[Main/en/NewGRF]] sets.

== Use ==

This feature is enabled by default. You can disable this patch through the [[Main/en/Advanced Settings/Vehicles#Enable wagon speed limits|configure patches --> vehicle]] window or use the following syntax in [[Main/en/openttd.cfg]]:

 [patches]
 wagon_speed_limits = false
